'''克雷格·格里斯佩'''（{{lang-en|Craig Gillespie}}，{{bd|1967年|9月1日}}）是一名[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]電影导演，以作品《[[伍德考克先生|伍德考克先生]]》（2007年）和《[[新天师斗僵尸|新天师斗僵尸]]》（2011年）聞名。

== 早年生活 ==

格里斯佩於[[悉尼|悉尼]]出生及成長，19岁时移居美國[[纽约市|纽约市]]<ref name=soon>{{cite web| url = http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=38096| title = Craig Gillespie's Big Comeback| accessdate = 2008-08-23| date = 2007-10-09| publisher = ComingSoon.net| first = Edward| last = Douglas| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080614235531/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=38096| archive-date = 2008-06-14| dead-url = no}}</ref>，在[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]的[[視覺藝術學院_(紐約)|視覺藝術學院]]学习插画、平面設計及广告设计<ref name=verve>{{cite press release|title=''Lars & the Real Girl'' Production Notes|publisher=Verve Pictures|url=http://www.vervepics.com/docs/larsnotes.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2008-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717194823/http://www.vervepics.com/docs/larsnotes.pdf|archive-date=2011-07-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=time>{{cite web| url = http://www.timeoutsydney.com.au/film/newsinterviews/finding-the-right-girl.aspx| title = Director – Craig Gillespie| accessdate = 2008-08-23| date = 2008-04-02| publisher = ''Time Out Sydney''| first = Ruth| last = Hessey| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090809122025/http://www.timeoutsydney.com.au/film/newsinterviews/finding-the-right-girl.aspx| archivedate = 2009-08-09}}</ref>。20多岁时，他首次對電影萌生興趣，當時格里斯佩的一位朋友成为电影导演，並鼓勵他做相同的事情<ref name=film>{{cite web| url = http://www.filmmakermagazine.com/directorinterviews/2007/10/craig-gillespie-lars-and-real-girl.php| title = CRAIG GILLESPIE, ''LARS AND THE REAL GIRL''| accessdate = 2008-08-23| date = 2007-10-12| publisher = ''{{link-en|Filmmaker (雜誌)|Filmmaker (magazine)|Filmmaker Magazine}}''| first = Nick| last = Dawson| archive-date = 2008-11-08| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081108233229/http://www.filmmakermagazine.com/directorinterviews/2007/10/craig-gillespie-lars-and-real-girl.php| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

== 事業 ==

格里斯佩工作了15年，以{{link-en|廣告導演|Commercial director}}為業，常與電影攝影師亞當·金摩和{{link-en|羅德里哥·普里托|Rodrigo Prieto}}一同工作<ref name=film/><ref name=LA>{{cite news| url = http://articles.latimes.com/2007/oct/02/entertainment/et-gold2| title = Hit or miss? Yes| accessdate = 2008-08-23| date = 2007-10-02| publisher = ''[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]''| first = Patrick| last = Goldstein| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081211075618/http://articles.latimes.com/2007/oct/02/entertainment/et-gold2| archive-date = 2008-12-11| dead-url = no}}</ref>。他經常變換[[廣告代理商|廣告代理商]]，曾在5年內為6個機構工作<ref name=oz>{{cite news| url = http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,,23468669-16947,00.html?from=public_rss| title = Dysfunction and the love doll| accessdate = 2008-08-23| date = 2008-04-02| publisher = ''[[澳洲人報|The Australian]]''| first = Michael| last = Bodey}}{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。他於{{link-en|第54屆美國導演工會獎|54th Directors Guild of America Awards|2001年}}及{{link-en|第55屆美國導演工會獎|55th Directors Guild of America Awards|2002年}}入圍由[[美國導演工會獎|美國導演工會獎]]所頒發的「最佳商業廣告導演獎」，並在{{link-en|第59屆美國導演工會獎|59th Directors Guild of America Awards|2006年}}以他為{{link-en|Ameriquest Mortgage|Ameriquest Mortgage}}和{{link-en|Altoids|Altoids}}公司所製作的廣告贏得該獎<ref name=verve/>。格里斯佩還在2005年的[[坎城國際創意節|坎城國際創意節]]上榮獲金獅獎，他的2件廣告作品屬於[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]][[曼哈頓中城|中城]][[現代藝術博物館|現代藝術博物館]]的永久收藏品<ref name=verve/>。

他執導的首部劇情長片為2007年的《[[伍德考克先生|伍德考克先生]]》。然而，他在進行幾次{{link-en|試映會|Test screening}}後退出劇組，許多場景重寫並重拍，{{link-en|大衛·多布金 (導演)|David Dobkin (director)|大衛·多布金}}取代了格里斯佩的導演職位。格里斯佩最初收到該劇本時，便認為觀眾對他在廣告中使用的黑色幽默會有很好的反響，但據他表示，「很明顯，觀眾希望一部更廣泛的喜劇片，而不是我拍的這一部。我很感謝新線影業的接手，所以我讓出職位。」<ref name=film/><ref name=LA/>《伍德考克先生》的[[主要攝影|主要攝影]]結束不到1個月，格里斯佩便開始了《[[充氣娃娃之戀|充氣娃娃之戀]]》的前期作業。此前他已持有劇本4年，但沒有任何劇組成員或工作室加盟<ref name=soon/>。在加盟《伍德考克先生》之前，格里斯佩就讀過了該劇本，《充氣娃娃之戀》的題材——一名愛上[[性愛娃娃|性愛娃娃]]的男人——讓他敬而遠之，認為這個前提是「荒謬的概念」<ref name=soon/>。他於是推辭掉了許多大型工作室，選擇優先執導《伍德考克先生》<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118016546.html?categoryid=1238&cs=1&query=fright+night|title=Gillespie signs on for 'Fright Night' 'Lars and the Real Girl' guy boards DreamWorks remake|first=Pamela|last=McClintock|publisher=Variety|date=2010-03-16|access-date=2017-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100325060509/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118016546.html?categoryid=1238&cs=1&query=fright+night|archive-date=2010-03-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

格里斯佩執導了[[史蒂芬·史匹柏|史蒂芬·史匹柏]]與[[迪亞布羅·科蒂|迪亞布羅·科蒂]]的電視劇《[[倒錯人生|倒錯人生]]》的第1季中的幾集（包含[[電視試播|試播集]]）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloody-disgusting.com/news/20223|title=DreamWorks Planning a 'Fright Night' in 3-D?|publisher=BloodyDisgusting|access-date=2017-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118033554/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/20223|archive-date=2017-01-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年，他有意執導電影《[[藥命俱樂部|藥命俱樂部]]》，並找上《充氣娃娃之戀》的主演[[雷恩·葛斯林|雷恩·葛斯林]]。該片講述{{link-en|羅恩·伍德羅夫|Ron Woodroof}}的真實故事，一名電工被診斷出患有愛滋病，僅剩下6個月的壽命，但他使用了走私給其他愛滋病患者的各種藥品，多活6年以上才離世<ref>{{cite news| url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117986885.html?categoryid=13| title = Gosling buys into Gillespie's 'Club'| accessdate =2008-08-23| date = 2008-06-04| publisher = ''[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]''| first = Michael| last = Fleming}}</ref>。然而，該片的導演最後由[[尚-馬克·瓦利|尚-馬克·瓦利]]擔任，而[[馬修·麥康納|馬修·麥康納]]則取代葛斯林飾演羅恩·伍德羅夫。

他與[[山姆·沃辛頓|山姆·沃辛頓]]榮獲2009年澳大利亞電影突破獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://australiansinfilm.org/australians-in-film-breakthrough-awards.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120703000026/http://australiansinfilm.org/australians-in-film-breakthrough-awards.html|archivedate=2012-07-03|title=Breakthrough Awards|work=Australians in Film|accessdate=2017-03-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2010年3月，格里斯佩宣布，他將執導《{{link-en|吸血鬼住在隔壁|Fright Night}}》（1985年）的重拍電影《[[吸血鬼就在隔壁|吸血鬼就在隔壁]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/36446/fright-night-remake-director-now-official|title=Fright Night Remake Director Now Official!|publisher=DreadCentral|access-date=2017-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714190411/http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/36446/fright-night-remake-director-now-official|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由[[柯林·法洛|柯林·法洛]]、[[安東·葉爾欽|安東·葉爾欽]]及[[東妮·克莉蒂|東妮·克莉蒂]]主演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/37884/more-fright-night-remake-location-location-location|title=More on the Fright Night Remake ... Location, Location, Location!|publisher=DreadCentral|access-date=2017-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714154542/http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/37884/more-fright-night-remake-location-location-location|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，他執導了[[基德·酷迪|基德·酷迪]]單曲《{{link-en|No One Believes Me|No One Believes Me}}》的[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]。2011年4月18日，格里斯佩簽約執導擔任小說《[[傲慢與偏見與殭屍|傲慢與偏見與殭屍]]》的[[傲慢與偏見與殭屍_(電影)|同名改編電影]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/04/19/pride-and-prejudice-and-zombies-director-exclusive/ |title='Pride and Prejudice and Zombies' director chews over Jane Austen mash-up – EXCLUSIVE |work=[[娛樂周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] |first=Anthony |last=Breznican |date=2011-04-19 |accessdate=2011-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110424035218/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/04/19/pride-and-prejudice-and-zombies-director-exclusive/ |archive-date=2011-04-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後於10月底退出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2011/10/craig-gillespie-exits-lionsgates-pride-and-prejudice-and-zombies-188100/|title=Craig Gillespie Exits Lionsgate's 'Pride And Prejudice And Zombies'|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|date=2011-10-27|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000442/https://deadline.com/2011/10/craig-gillespie-exits-lionsgates-pride-and-prejudice-and-zombies-188100/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由{{le|伯爾·史緹爾|Burr Steers}}接手<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2013/film/news/lily-collins-pride-prejudice-zombies-1200435950/|title='Pride, Prejudice and Zombies' Resurrected With Lily Collins and Director Burr Steers (EXCLUSIVE)|author=Kroll, Justin|date=2013-05-01|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-date=2020-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200406201856/https://variety.com/2013/film/news/lily-collins-pride-prejudice-zombies-1200435950/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年4月，宣布格里斯佩將執導電影《絕命救援》，該片講述海岸防衛隊的人員於1952年試圖救援2艘油輪的船員，[[克里斯·潘恩|克里斯·潘恩]]、[[凱西·艾佛列克|凱西·艾佛列克]]、[[喬許·史都華|喬許·史都華]]、[[葛拉罕·麥克塔維什|葛拉罕·麥克塔維什]]及[[凱爾·加納|凱爾·加納]]擔任主演，[[華特迪士尼影業|華特迪士尼影業]]製片<ref>{{cite news|title=Chris Pine in Talks to Star in Disney's 'Finest Hours'|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/chris-pine-in-talks-to-star-in-disneys-finest-hours-1201159228/|publisher=variety.com|access-date=2017-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331210001/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/chris-pine-in-talks-to-star-in-disneys-finest-hours-1201159228/|archive-date=2017-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Casey Affleck In 'Finest Hours' Talks|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/08/casey-affleck-in-finest-hours-talks/|accessdate=2014-08-07|publisher=deadline.com|date=2014-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140807094858/http://www.deadline.com/2014/08/casey-affleck-in-finest-hours-talks/|archive-date=2014-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title='Dark Knight Rises' Actor Josh Stewart Joins Chris Pine in 'Finest Hours'|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/josh-stewart-finest-hours-chris-pine-1201289927/|publisher=variety.com|access-date=2017-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140831010822/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/josh-stewart-finest-hours-chris-pine-1201289927/|archive-date=2014-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title='The Finest Hours' Adds 'Outlander's Graham McTavish|url=http://deadline.com/2014/08/lake-bell-jack-kilmer-graham-mctavish-824354/|publisher=deadline.com|access-date=2017-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140909001114/http://deadline.com/2014/08/lake-bell-jack-kilmer-graham-mctavish-824354/|archive-date=2014-09-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title='Kyle Gallner Joins Disaster-At-Sea Drama 'The Finest Hours'|url=http://deadline.com/2014/09/kyle-gallner-the-finest-hours-disney-movie-831634/|publisher=deadline.com|access-date=2017-03-31|archive-url=https:/